review_blob: i dont really think this should already be out pretty early but w/e i saw it and couldnt resist lol. not nearly as good as i remember tho. 6 pack of bottles. changed all the labeling and boxing this year. dark amber pour. off white head. very little lacing if any. little to no aroma or after taste u can only smell a little bit of spices. slightly malty, bready, caramely and mildly fruity. very middle beer i expected much more. theese ratings are crazy lol. i wish i would have spent this 10 bucks on a 90+ beer instead of this crap=\.
